---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken with Smashed Potatoes, Roasted Green Beans and Rosemary Pan Sauce
description: Crispy chicken, a luscious pan sauce, chunky smashed potatoes and fresh green beans make for a savoury dish that's comforting and will stick to your ribs!
